OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely sunny and dry this
OL,6,Fmorning and becoming widely very warm
OL,7,For hot again, away from cooler and
OL,8,Fbreezier coastal areas. Generally
OL,9,Fturning cloudier during the afternoon
OL,10,Fwith scattered showers developing,
OL,11,Fthese could be accompanied by some
OL,12,Fthunder at times.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FAny showers or thunderstorms
OL,15,Feasing and skies clearing to leave a
OL,16,Ffine, dry night. Warm overnight for
OL,17,Fmany eastern areas, although feeling
OL,18,Fslightly fresher in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
