OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSome early sunshine likely,
OL,6,Falthough cloud increasing from the
OL,7,Fwest brings a risk of showers, perhaps
OL,8,Fthundery. A slightly cooler day for
OL,9,Fmany areas, but still generally very
OL,10,Fwarm.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,13,Flargely sunny and very warm or hot on
OL,14,FSaturday. Trending cooler and more
OL,15,Fchangeable from Sunday. An increased
OL,16,Fchance of rain, but still some fine,
OL,17,Fwarm weather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
